{"tid":1290384,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[推薦] 凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰紀錄片","createTime":"2019-07-06T12:59:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T15:48:48.000Z","uid":212274,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"84e3a4b6ea3286c44d3c2906aa9e794e8b675fa6","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2942042/org/599e2c54b5e0ebc6bd7bb7fadf27b63a.jpg/GP5KwRB2JBgkFxPESN1NdXaTd2vfPaSWZPc9imT3PYo?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2942042%2Forg%2F599e2c54b5e0ebc6bd7bb7fadf27b63a.jpg%2FGP5KwRB2JBgkFxPESN1NdXaTd2vfPaSWZPc9imT3PYo%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=87275b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNetflix: <a href=\"https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.netflix.com%2Fhk%2Ftitle%2F80031666&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=7393cf53\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.netflix.com/hk/title/80031666</a><br />\n革命背景(HK01): <a href=\"https://bit.ly/32f4s39\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F32f4s39&d=Yo3BLZp%2B9L0ow7gqQKw5zZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=8d82628b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/32f4s39</a><br />\n<br />\n《凜冬烈火：烏克蘭自由之戰》曾入圍第88屆奧斯卡金像獎最佳紀錄片獎，由俄國導演Evgeny Afineevsky執導，而其實導演與團隊也是親歷這場運動之中。透過鏡頭可以看到2014年在烏克蘭一場由示威遊行、抗爭、之後演變成近武裝革命的運動，當中捕捉到很多危險的現場畫面，根本與戰地攝影沒太大分別。<br />\n<br />\n靜係睇預告已經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係睇到人地個決心係好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望香港即使2047果陣都唔洗變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d666f698a4787bf1869007c9ea5675ae0571520c","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:00:41.000Z","msg":"當時烏克蘭失業率高、官員貪污嚴重，此舉令不少人民深信情況，只會每況愈下，經濟會雪上加霜。所以有人號召民眾去到獨立廣場抗議，人民決心走上街動發聲。起初聚集的群眾以年輕人為主，有很多大學生。他們在獨立廣場唱歌、跳舞，就似一個嘉年華一樣。當時不少年輕人都指，自己對未來有很大的期待，他們是來到獨立廣場實踐夢想，那時的口號是「烏克蘭屬於歐洲」。"},{"pid":"e0064374f68766418a878d2283e6b0d2a35e14c8","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"然而，政府漠視民眾的訴求，沒有作出回應。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>遊行的第九天，口號變成了「請回應我們的訴求！」但烏克蘭政府卻進行第一次清場，廣場上鮮血淋漓，政府授權軍力及警力開始使用暴力驅逐。</strong></span>群眾感到絕望，原本保家衛國的士兵，毫不留情地毆打人民；保護人民的警察，竟變成是人民殺手。人民無奈地背着傷痕退出獨立廣場。"},{"pid":"cb4bd0a99e357da91b03c1eb42ffde6d2459798d","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:03:09.000Z","msg":"群眾第二次決定再奪回獨立廣場時，號召了更多人參與，同時政府也準備好足夠彈藥，出動更激進的特種部隊，更全力進攻獨立廣場清場。附近有教堂取得主教的祝福後，敲響教堂的鐘，有民眾呼喚更多人來對抗特種部隊以及支援示威人士。最後有一萬多名市民前來增援，守住獨立廣場。<br />\n雙方對峙愈演愈烈，持續有人民出現傷亡，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">特種部隊在街上射殺民眾，甚至衝入急救站殺害醫生、救護人員等。</span></strong>事情一直到2014年2月，亞努科維奇出逃，政權瓦解。"},{"pid":"784ccbfd4b3473aa246c9d974a230eef5481f15a","tid":1290384,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"香港唯一分別 : 無兵役及專業軍事知識"},{"pid":"5ead3446244ae3f6ab79029ad4e7dc71557607f7","tid":1290384,"uid":263058,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:04:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8351cb6a54337c4311a6d7ae780d9133cc28958a","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"784ccbfd4b3473aa246c9d974a230eef5481f15a","tid":1290384,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:03:29.000Z","msg":"香港唯一分別 : 無兵役及專業軍事知識"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"就算有都應該好難去到呢種地步<br />\n宜家仲有好多廢老見到新聞影到著曬防具帶口罩就話一定出去攪事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連武器都無都可以話你暴徙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4466d1a73a0999fd4a5a389aeffe500ea2d0e1f","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:14:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705b17a3d1cd610885e2e0beecb0779d14233e75","tid":1290384,"uid":249187,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:15:25.000Z","msg":"琴日睇完，覺得好震撼，佩服佢地既勇氣之餘亦驚訝佢地情況同香港驚人地相似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好推薦大家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"511427723c5cd23f12fdd09d06a615fe5fdc97c8","tid":1290384,"uid":212274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T13:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a9a51e89a7955b805b0d5c971824b2b6641d61","tid":1290384,"uid":156326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:07:21.000Z","msg":"非常推薦 睇到好震撼"},{"pid":"b992660e315b3ddfcaef292a94db5bbd7d88dcf2","tid":1290384,"uid":247482,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:09:26.000Z","msg":"睇完就會覺得烏克蘭都唔算太勇武<br />\n<br />\n如果係香港立條同樣既反示威法，一樣打到飛起"},{"pid":"63bca0d842100a69063b976b56de566425cd2c6d","tid":1290384,"uid":9846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T14:19:27.000Z","msg":"有一幕講政府立法以唔容許人戴頭盔、汽車唔可以兩三架一齊行去唔比人示威，睇到呢幕就諗起藍絲講話要立法唔比戴口罩同頭盔，如果政府真係咁做，我諗香港人真係唔會再等呢個政府嘅回應"},{"pid":"e8a4e5845295333e8ab545c0bfdf4648df2873fd","tid":1290384,"uid":2322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:17:28.000Z","msg":"<code>我無嘢講 我要見律師 我唔解鎖電話 我唔簽任何文件 我要去醫院驗傷</code>"},{"pid":"8c545d0dbfe58709cc6592da6f51a801cc337786","tid":1290384,"uid":2322,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T18:18:20.000Z","msg":"琴晚睇完 好值得參考"},{"pid":"68b41da4ff1a9c71037ca48aa6e635bf34886484","tid":1290384,"uid":159960,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T03:46:27.000Z","msg":"反親俄根本係反親中既一面鏡<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.wuyibox.com/d/file/uploads/cegknprvyzAEKMVY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.wuyibox.com%2Fd%2Ffile%2Fuploads%2Fcegk