-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpixhost.icu%2Favaxhome%2F04%2F28%2F00652804.jpg&h=9b648fe0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/2016-02-12-16_15_59-694x387.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2F2016-02-12-16_15_59-694x387.png&h=9aad7efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://2static.fjcdn.com/large/pictures/2f/0f/2f0f20_5739347.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F2static.fjcdn.com%2Flarge%2Fpictures%2F2f%2F0f%2F2f0f20_5739347.jpg&h=38de3698&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T11:12:24.000Z","msg":"睇到佢地成功左真心覺得等佢地開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"490101e9e698982f6ec70a16686e7befa4dca666","tid":1290384,"uid":9214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T15:48:48.000Z","msg":"烏克蘭係香港嘅未來<br />\n警察變得冷血冇人性<br />\n親政府嘅人可以任意攻擊人<br />\n就連普通人老弱都唔放<br />\n香港正正發生緊<br />\n<br />\n佢地同我地一樣對抗嘅都係共產主義<br />\n革命必須血洗<br />\n要有心理準備"}]}